## What I Worked On Today

Task A-5 involves the ISSO and IT Administrator reviewing the SAR findings, determining which items to remediate before the authorization package is finalized, executing those remediations with full change management documentation, verifying each remediation with the assessor, and updating the SAR and POA&M to reflect the post-remediation state.

I also worked on the communication piece — drafting the remediation status update for the AO that documents what was fixed, what remains in the POA&M, and why the remaining items are appropriate for post-authorization tracking rather than pre-authorization remediation.

