### Finding A-7: IAM Entity Creation Added to CM-3 Notification Triggers — REMEDIATED

**Original finding:** The CM-3 change management procedure did not list IAM entity creation as a required ISSO-notification change category, enabling the A-3 service account to be created without ISSO awareness.

**Remediation decision:** Fix before authorization. This is the root cause of A-3 — if we remediate A-3 without A-7, the same pattern can recur. The fix is a procedure document update plus an automated EventBridge notification rule. Both are low effort.

**Remediation executed:**

*Step 1 — Update CM-3 procedure:*
ISSO updated the change management procedure to add IAM entity creation (CreateUser, CreateRole, CreateGroup, CreateServiceLinkedRole) to the required ISSO-notification change category list. Updated procedure approved by Health IT Manager. Version updated. Change log reference: CM-CHG-[number].

*Step 2 — Implement automated IAM creation notification:*
ISSO created AWS EventBridge rule: source = `aws.iam`; event type = `AWS API Call via CloudTrail`; detail type = CreateUser OR CreateRole OR CreateGroup. Target: SNS topic → ISSO email and SMS. Rule tested [date] by creating and immediately deleting a test IAM user — SNS notification received within 45 seconds. Test record in remediation evidence package Section R-2.

*Step 3 — Brief IT Administrator:*
ISSO conducted a 15-minute conversation with the IT Administrator reviewing the updated procedure and the new automated notification. IT Administrator confirmed understanding that all IAM entity creation requires ISSO notification and that the automated rule will now generate an alert regardless of whether the notification is done manually. Record in ISSO communication log [date].

**Post-remediation verification:** EventBridge rule [openmrs-iam-creation-alert] — Active status confirmed. Test notification receipt documented. Procedure document version history shows update [date].

**Assessor verification:** Remediation evidence submitted to assessor [date]. Assessor confirmed Finding A-7 resolved — SAR updated: Resolved pre-authorization.

